name: Allison Harvard ‘Insensate’ Alternate Poster
description: Photograph by Optera of the three leads in filmmaker Julie Schuldt’s 2012 cult film ‘Insensate’. From left to right: Shelby Benson, Allison Harvard, Monika Mercedes. Photo was taken in late winter of 2011 in Amstrong Redwoods State Natural Reserve in Sonoma County, California, at the end of the day the film wrapped. Though it captures well the mood of the film, it was ultimately decided the photograph was too dark for use as the official poster.
